Name: resource-name
Description: the name of a sound file, or prefab, etc.

Name: source
Description: Can be built-in, primitive, online, or prefab

Name: color
Description: Color is an array of comma separated integers/floats representing the RGB

Name: size
Description: (for now) A string of comma separated values  representing the scaling in each direction

Name: vector
Description: a string of comma separated ints or floats representing a position in space
